This paper explores a reputation system for multi-agent marketplaces, which involves concepts from multi-agent systems, game theory, cybersecurity, and complex systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems), followed by cs.GT (Game Theory), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
